Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}后面尘土大起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.67,0:02:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}估计是曹操的追兵到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}云长 子龙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即刻布阵 准备迎战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三弟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.78,0:03:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你随我去会会他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许将军
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备已经摆好阵势了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.16,0:03:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要打便打 爷不怕他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相命我们召回刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:04:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}并没有让我们厮杀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果刘备不肯奉命 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那也不可厮杀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们只有五百人马
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可他们有五万
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你说怎么办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请将军在这儿领兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我过去给刘备传命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有我的命令万万不可过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:05:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}文远将军何故到此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奉丞相命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请刘皇叔回朝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朝廷另有任用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将在外 君命有所不受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何况现在袁术兵马已动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}军情如火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我应速速赶往徐州阻击他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.18,0:05:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}万万不可失了戎机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这么说 刘皇叔不肯回朝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不回
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请将军代我向丞相禀报
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.59,0:05:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就说刘备不会辜负了丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更不会辜负了朝廷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}张将军 我以为敌军来袭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以预先布好了阵势
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:05:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原来是张将军到来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虚惊了一场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要不是你拦着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我早就和他们厮杀起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么也别说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}见丞相再说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.49,0:06:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}张辽 许褚 到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相 禀丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备拒绝回朝廷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他说将在外君命有所不受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.11,0:07:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他说他急着赶往徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去截杀袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.58,0:07:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}托辞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备还说什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备还说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}戎机不可失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他说他绝对不会辜负丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.89,0:07:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更不会辜负朝廷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备这厮还摆下阵势
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将本想厮杀 张辽不让
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}张辽做得对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相 刘备杭命不归
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.90,0:08:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其心思已经昭然可知啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拖至将来会更加麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不如立刻派大军剿杀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}程昱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我越来越觉得用刘备是用对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.70,0:08:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备此次出征
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}必能截杀袁术替我除一大害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我料他不敢反
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.91,0:08:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为我有朱灵 路昭二将随征
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那五万人马归他们掌控
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.02,0:08:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不归刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第三
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我历来用人都是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}疑人不用 用人不疑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:09:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然用了 岂能后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果刘备敢反
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正好给我一个取他首级的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}程昱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎么老是叹息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备抗命不归
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我劝主公派大军征剿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公非但不听
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还哈哈大笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他越想越觉得用刘备用对了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.51,0:09:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你听这话 荒唐不荒唐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看主公不荒唐 是你荒唐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:09:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.69,0:10:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你想想 刘备已经领兵跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你再派大军去征剿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那不是一误再误吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们当前的大敌是袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不能节外生枝 再树强敌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然木已成舟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就让刘备这只舟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让他替我们去截杀袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们就可以集中力量对付袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先生所言极是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可主公也是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明错了 却不认错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其实主公的心里早就知道错了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.61,0:10:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}日后他也会改错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但他永远不会认错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何谓人主
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就是 知错 改错 不认错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}万万不可认错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 末将已查明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.11,0:11:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术就藏于这座庙中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.01,0:11:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}残兵不过百人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥 给我一炷香的功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我保证手到擒来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那袁术也算是一方诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果擒回许昌 太过折辱他了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样吧 我写一封手书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}子龙送进庙中 面呈袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让他自己斟酌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大哥你就是心善
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}忘了袁术那厮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:11:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当年如何欺负人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.31,0:12:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}断了咱们的粮饷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.51,0:12:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}渴死朕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还不赶快去找蜜水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 现在都是血水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有蜜水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.62,0:12:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}皇上 皇上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.62,0:12:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}外面来了位将军
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}左将军刘备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有书呈袁公路将军
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}公路将军如晤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备奉命生擒将军
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}解往许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但备为君着想 别有不忍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日 惟盼君自决 不辱威名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.00,0:13:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备拜上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备还是个忠厚人哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下 陛下 主公 主公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.62,0:14:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀主公
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁术自裁啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}古往今来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有多少英雄豪杰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:15:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都被这块石头害死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}罪将朱灵叩告丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备令罪将把这传国玉玺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}带回来献给主公
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}却扣下了五万兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说是用来驻守徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.01,0:15:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以防袁绍大军攻袭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州原本就是我的 我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.22,0:15:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我自有车胄将军把守
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}干刘备何事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}五万兵马如何丢失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.03,0:15:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}张飞设酒宴把罪将等都给灌醉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等我醒来时 已被绑在了车上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备令我把这玉玺献给丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.81,0:16:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要它何用 推出去斩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.12,0:16:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相 饶命啊 丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相 饶命啊丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.23,0:16:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹仁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末将在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.23,0:16:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即刻给车胄增兵三万
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.64,0:16:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让他严防徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}告诉他 刘备胆敢来攻城
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即刻擒杀 提头来见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.81,0:16:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}报 报 禀丞相 据败兵回报
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州已经被刘备占据
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}守将车胄也被关羽斩杀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}徐州各郡都已陷入刘备手中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.04,0:16:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可能 绝对不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.94,0:16:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}车胄有八万精兵驻防徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}八万呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你就算是八万个馒头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备也得啃上半个月
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么可能说丢就丢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相 完全有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相 刘备奉命出师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他手中有一枚你颁给的兵符
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.93,0:17:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他很可能用此兵符
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}骗开徐州城门
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}车胄将军见此兵符以后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还以为刘备是丞相派来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.94,0:18:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相 快传太医
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父亲 父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.44,0:18:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丕儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.45,0:18:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孩儿在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我病了几日了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三日
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那病养得也差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我给你的几部兵书
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:19:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你可曾认真研修
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.63,0:19:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孩儿正在研修
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.34,0:19:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可怠慢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兵法之道 变化无常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.14,0:19:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既要熟读兵书又不能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.15,0:19:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被兵法所缚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}过两日我要听你心得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孩儿明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}植儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.43,0:19:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孩儿在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.13,0:19:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}近日可做了些好诗文吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.53,0:19:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}儿与稽康 孔融等宾客
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都有诗文唱和
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.74,0:19:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.94,0:19:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}过两日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.14,0:19:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 就今日下午
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.05,0:19:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拿来念我听听
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.32,0:19:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好诗文胜过灵丹妙药
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:20:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}孩儿遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吉平
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吉平在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你据实说 我这病况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相 你患的头痛病
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}时日已久了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}平时无大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是一旦动怒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.04,0:20:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}便会突发
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还望丞相安心静养啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是已经养了三日了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相 还需静养三十日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.55,0:20:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}天子若得知我得了徐州
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.75,0:21:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}定然会龙心大悦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不但徐州城重回到我们的手里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还增添了九万多兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}子龙正在抓紧训练
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}军容不俗 群情振奋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.84,0:21:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}子龙不但有悍将之勇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更有大将之才
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}告诉他让他加紧操练
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不出二十日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操必定来犯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}糜芳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}劳你去冀州晋见袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.42,0:21:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将此信交给他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.33,0:21:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一者 传达天子血诏旨意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.23,0:21:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请他快快发兵 勤王剿贼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二者告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无论他何日起兵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.94,0:21:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备都愿意听其号令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:21:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}甘当麾下先锋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公现已雄踞四州之地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.65,0:22:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}粮草军饷大为富足
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.55,0:22:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兵甲百万 战将千员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.45,0:22:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即使刘备不传天子诏书
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.66,0:22:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公也应当举兵征伐曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.99,0:22:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以求一统天下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.83,0:22:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下再强调一句
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.33,0:22:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公举兵灭曹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.93,0:22:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}并不是为了朝不保夕的天子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更不是为了扶汉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.43,0:22:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而是为了主公自己的君王大业
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.84,0:22:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 主公刚刚战罢公孙瓒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.04,0:22:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三军尚未得到休整
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且人困马乏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.05,0:22:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}加上近年来连年征战
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.55,0:22:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}使得所属各州焦土一片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.05,0:22:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}地无庄稼 民不聊生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.65,0:22:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}郭图所言 粮草军饷大为富足
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.06,0:22:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是纸上画饼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.56,0:22:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是簿册上的税赋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.73,0:22:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果要真把这些收入仓里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.93,0:22:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用于军旅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.23,0:22:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那没个三 五年的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.13,0:22:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是万万不可的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.13,0:22:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣建议 主公休兵养民
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.24,0:23:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}待军力民力充沛后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.74,0:23:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再行举兵伐曹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.24,0:23:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}禀主公 田丰所言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.55,0:23:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真乃书生之见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.25,0:23:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}眼下 主公兵锋正盛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.95,0:23:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三军斗志昂扬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.45,0:23:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}凭主公之神武 将士之昂扬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.46,0:23:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许昌指日可下 灭曹易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请主公即刻发兵 不可犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.23,0:23:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更不可迁延时日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.83,0:23:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}郭图所言 那是匹夫之勇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.63,0:23:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}古往今来 但能成就霸业者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.54,0:23:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}并不是依靠着他们的兵甲多寡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.54,0:23:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也不是依靠着攻城拔寨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.24,0:23:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而是依靠着国力 民力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.64,0:23:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}依靠着土地能长多少庄稼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.95,0:23:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们身后有多少子民
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.45,0:23:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}归根到底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.75,0:23:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}打仗拼得就是国力 民力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.65,0:23:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.86,0:23:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}坐拥冀 青 幽 并四大州
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.16,0:23:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而曹操只有兖州四郡和淮南一部
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.83,0:24:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总体实力不及主公一半
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.03,0:24:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公只需整军养民 富强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.24,0:24:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}静观天下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.34,0:24:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三年后再取曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.54,0:24:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那可真是如泰山压顶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.84,0:24:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}势不可挡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.75,0:24:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.25,0:24:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许攸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.96,0:24:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.56,0:24:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.26,0:24:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}郭图主张我举兵伐曹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.43,0:24:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}田丰主张我休养生息
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.44,0:24:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你意如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.04,0:24:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回主公
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.44,0:24:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚才郭图田丰二位大人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.95,0:24:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们的争论 在下听明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.45,0:24:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下以为 无论是战是和
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.16,0:25:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们都不能仅仅只看自家的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.46,0:25:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还要看一看敌人的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.16,0:25:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不仅要知道敌人最怕什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.96,0:25:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也要知道敌人最想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.23,0:25:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正可谓兵家云
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.54,0:25:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知彼知己 方能百战不殆
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.84,0:25:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下以为
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.45,0:25:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那曹操现在最想太平
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.35,0:25:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}且最怕交战
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.35,0:25:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为我家主公
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.95,0:25:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雄踞冀 青 幽 并四州
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.35,0:25:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可谓地大物博 兵强马壮
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.86,0:25:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在当今天下诸侯中
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.16,0:25:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}独站峰巅
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.16,0:25:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操呢 虽力不及主公
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.94,0:25:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可他却处在一个上升的时期
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.44,0:25:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所谓上升时期嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.84,0:25:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就更需要维持相对的稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.74,0:25:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以求得发展
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.55,0:25:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 如果我们也休养生息
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.35,0:26:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}表面看似对我们有利
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.95,0:26:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}实则是对那曹操更加有利
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.42,0:26:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为曹操比主公
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.56,0:26:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更需要时间来发展壮大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.96,0:26:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.37,0:26:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此时此刻正是敌我双方实力
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.84,0:26:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相差最大的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.34,0:26:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}实属天赐良机 千载难逢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.75,0:26:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果主公迁延日久
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.35,0:26:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我们只有坐观那曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.15,0:26:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一日日壮大起来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.76,0:26:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最后与主公并立于世
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.86,0:26:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}主公 要真到那时
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.97,0:26:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这胜负可就难料了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.34,0:27:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我心已定 立即发兵灭曹
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.35,0:27:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我等敬奉主公号令
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.65,0:27:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听令
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.96,0:27:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}着许攸 郭图为军师
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.56,0:27:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}颜良 文丑为大将
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.76,0:27:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}起马军十五万 步军十五万
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.26,0:27:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}进军黎阳
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.47,0:27:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.77,0:27:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陈琳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.27,0:27:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.74,0:27:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是我们这里最有才华的才子了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.05,0:27:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}着你替我拟写一道讨贼檄文
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.85,0:27:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}布告天下
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.76,0:27:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在下遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.06,0:27:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.46,0:27:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明主图危以制变
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.16,0:27:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}忠臣虑难以立权
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.67,0:27:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是以有非常之人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.77,0:28:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后有非常之事
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.07,0:28:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有非常之事
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.57,0:28:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后建非常之功
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.34,0:28:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司空曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.85,0:28:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其祖父曹腾
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.95,0:28:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昔为宫闱奸宦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.45,0:28:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}饕餮放纵 伤化虐民
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.95,0:28:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其父曹嵩 贪如豺 刁如蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.76,0:28:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}毒如蝎 狠如狼
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.16,0:28:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹氏一门
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.26,0:28:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从祖到孙尽为赘阉遗丑
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.86,0:28:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}腐臭勾当
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.07,0:28:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大将军袁绍奉汉威灵
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.77,0:28:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}折冲宙宇 长戟百万 健骑千群
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.27,0:28:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}并州越太行
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.17,0:28:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 好文章
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.25,0:28:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}势如奔马 气贯长虹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.95,0:28:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是难得一见的好文章
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.15,0:28:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们俩也看看
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.26,0:28:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这个陈琳堪称天下奇才
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.92,0:28:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雄视古今的大手笔
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.26,0:28:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就这一篇檄文
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.06,0:29:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抵得上十万大军啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.27,0:29:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹植 曹植
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.07,0:29:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你为何就写不出这等文章来
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.28,0:29:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你府上的那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.48,0:29:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不也是号称饱学之士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.95,0:29:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我看都是酒囊饭袋
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.65,0:29:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有你 好高鹜远
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.15,0:29:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没有真才实学
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.86,0:29:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父亲责备的是 孩儿惭愧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.56,0:29:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}传命各级文武 大堂议政
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.66,0:29:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父亲 父亲 那你的病还没好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.87,0:29:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陈琳的这篇檄文
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.87,0:29:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是灵丹妙药啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.77,0:29:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给我惊出一身冷汗来
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.37,0:29:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}头风早好了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.18,0:29:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍地广民丰 带甲百万
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.25,0:29:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}文臣武将更是数不胜数
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.05,0:29:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如许攸 郭图 田丰 逄纪等人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.35,0:29:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都是智谋超群
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.96,0:30:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}颜良 文丑 张郃 淳于琼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.66,0:30:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也都是当世名将
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.16,0:30:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相不可与袁绍交战
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.56,0:30:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只可与袁绍议和
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.27,0:30:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相 先生所言
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.57,0:30:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真乃腐儒之见 依我看
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.88,0:30:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍有十败 丞相有十胜
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.05,0:30:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}愿闻其详
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.75,0:30:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍喜欢繁复礼仪
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.05,0:30:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相喜欢自然天成
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.46,0:30:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此为道胜
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.36,0:30:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍以异逆动 丞相爱顺势
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.86,0:30:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此为义胜
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.86,0:30:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍以宽济 丞相以猛纠
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.77,0:30:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此为治胜
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.27,0:30:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍外宽内忌 任人唯亲
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.57,0:30:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相外简内明 任人唯才
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.98,0:30:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此为度胜
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.18,0:31:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍多谋少决 丞相多谋善断
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.15,0:31:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此为谋胜
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.85,0:31:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍嗜好虚名 丞相以诚待士
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.96,0:31:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此为德胜
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.66,0:31:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍忽近忽远 丞相远近皆察
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.17,0:31:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此为仁胜
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.07,0:31:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍听信谗言 丞相洞若观火
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.17,0:31:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此为明胜
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.18,0:31:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍是非混淆 丞相法度严谨
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.68,0:31:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此为文胜
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.08,0:31:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍好大喜功 不知兵法
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.19,0:31:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相以少克众 用兵如神
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.46,0:31:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此为武胜
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.96,0:31:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍有此十败 丞相有此十胜
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.66,0:31:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然战端未开
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.66,0:31:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣以为胜负已定
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.28,0:32:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.98,0:32:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}战和之争就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.15,0:32:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你等回营速速整军
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.86,0:32:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}五日之后
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.86,0:32:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要自亲率二十万大军
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.46,0:32:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}迎战袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.47,0:32:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下 大喜呀
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.87,0:32:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刘备已收复徐州 得兵九万
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.38,0:32:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}并且把陛下的诏书传给了袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.98,0:32:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍发出了讨贼檄文
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.18,0:32:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}诏告天下
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.89,0:32:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}举三十万大军征讨曹贼
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.46,0:32:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.36,0:32:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}袁绍和刘备的义军
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.46,0:32:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何时进入许昌
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.36,0:32:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这 这是早晚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.27,0:33:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过陛下不可太心急
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.97,0:33:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣有一计
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.98,0:33:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}与袁刘大军里应外合
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.08,0:33:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一举定天下
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.28,0:33:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}爱卿有何妙计
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.79,0:33:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有一位密友 名叫吉平
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.29,0:33:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在他是宫廷太医
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.36,0:33:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正为曹操治病
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.26,0:33:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}此人世受国恩
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.76,0:33:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}深怀报国大志啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.88,0:33:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}斩除国贼
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.58,0:33:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}何需袁 刘那些兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.59,0:33:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要在下一举手
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.69,0:33:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}便可取曹操的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.26,0:33:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操身边甲士如云
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.06,0:34:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}外人根本无法接近
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.97,0:34:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兄台为何如此自信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.17,0:34:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我哪里是什么外人哪
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.47,0:34:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这几日
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.67,0:34:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我几乎成了曹操的贴身侍卫
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.78,0:34:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}每次他犯头风
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.38,0:34:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都要唤我去相府为其治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.38,0:34:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要我在药罐里下上一剂毒药
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.09,0:34:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹操便会一命呜呼
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.56,0:34:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}即使你成功地毒死了曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.57,0:34:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自己不是也会被杀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.27,0:34:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不妥 不妥
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.78,0:34:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为国捐躯 死得其所
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.08,0:34:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣世世代代饱受国恩
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.29,0:35:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今陛下有难
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.19,0:35:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为臣者 何惜此命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.57,0:35:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.67,0:35:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下得吉平兄相助
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.17,0:35:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真乃天降福音 社稷大幸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.88,0:35:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要曹操一死
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.28,0:35:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}许昌城便是群龙无首
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.68,0:35:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所有的文臣武将们
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.88,0:35:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只能拥戴陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.19,0:35:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那时
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.19,0:35:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}陛下定将吉平兄的灵位
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.89,0:35:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}供于功臣阁中
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.39,0:35:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}与高祖帝为伴
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.80,0:35:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}享受万世供奉
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.27,0:35:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妹子 妹子 哥来了 快快快
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.57,0:35:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小声点 你别让主子听见了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.28,0:35:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.28,0:35:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妹子 哥想死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.98,0:35:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小声点 别让主子听见
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.08,0:36:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哥想死你了 妹子
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.40,0:36:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}狗男女 作孽呀
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.47,0:36:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}给我拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.47,0:36:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.87,0:36:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}饶了我吧 饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.77,0:36:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在柴房行禽兽之事
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.27,0:36:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被奴才当场拿获
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.48,0:36:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请主公发落
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.18,0:36:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}伤风败俗 玷污我家风
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.38,0:36:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这等禽兽留他何用
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.29,0:36:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}锁下了 天明处死
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.49,0:36:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}带走
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.89,0:36:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老爷 老爷饶命吧 老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.19,0:36:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老爷 饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.50,0:36:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老爷饶了小的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.50,0:36:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老爷饶命啊老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.60,0:36:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小的知错了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.40,0:37:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相的头疾发作了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.70,0:37:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相的头疾犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.80,0:37:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快 快去请太医吉平
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.70,0:37:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快 你 你去请吉平
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.17,0:37:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快 快去 快跑 跑 快去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.08,0:37:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吉平 药熬好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.78,0:37:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就好 就好
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.18,0:38:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相 汤药好了 你请用药
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.79,0:38:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太烫了 搁那儿凉会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.88,0:38:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吉平你做太医多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.88,0:38:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣是初平二年进宫从医的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.18,0:38:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}算起来有十三个年头了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.69,0:38:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}初平二年
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.39,0:38:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那年我也干了一件惊天动地的事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.30,0:39:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你知道什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.10,0:39:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}臣不知
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.80,0:39:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那年的三月八日
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.11,0:39:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那天董卓也像我一样躺在榻上
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.38,0:39:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我哪 怀揣七星刀
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.28,0:39:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}慢慢地向他逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.99,0:39:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想要为国除凶 青史留名
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.29,0:39:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没想到董卓从镜子里发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.60,0:39:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}害得我险些丧命
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.90,0:39:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我更没有想到的是
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.70,0:39:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今日我也被人看成董卓了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.48,0:39:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相 汤药凉了药力会大减
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.99,0:39:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请丞相用药
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.29,0:40:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上古有礼
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.20,0:40:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}君患疾饮药 臣先尝之
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.20,0:40:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}父患疾饮药 子先尝之
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.61,0:40:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你待我如君如父
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.71,0:40:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就请你先尝尝此药吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.18,0:40:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这 丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.78,0:40:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大胆 拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.19,0:40:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说 谁令你下毒的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.90,0:40:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁是你的同党
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.30,0:40:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是我要杀贼 何须别人指使
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.10,0:40:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你一个小小的太医
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.31,0:40:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}岂敢下毒害我
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.41,0:40:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说出你的同党我不杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.01,0:40:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曹贼 天下人人得以诛之
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.88,0:41:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}岂止吉平
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.58,0:41:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}拖下去 严刑拷问
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.19,0:41:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}务必问出主使人是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.19,0:41:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.49,0:41:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}国贼 国贼
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.19,0:41:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人人得以诛之 国贼
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.10,0:41:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.90,0:41:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}赶快开门 开门
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.20,0:41:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来了 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.41,0:41:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相有请车骑将军董承赴宴
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.71,0:41:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请回禀丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.91,0:41:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我家主公卧病在床
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.11,0:41:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相事先就盼咐了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.18,0:41:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说 如果董承称病
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.89,0:41:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也一定请他抱病前来
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.99,0:41:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}快去 去呀
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.69,0:41:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请将军稍候 我去禀报主公
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.10,0:41:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}两个月前 我还在此青梅煮酒
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.31,0:41:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}与刘备笑论天下英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.91,0:42:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如今情形不再
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.91,0:42:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}秋风落叶 树木凋零啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.79,0:42:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}连那刘备也反了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.79,0:42:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过我看无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.60,0:42:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}秋风落叶也可一赏
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.90,0:42:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}枯木寒窗也可助兴
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.41,0:42:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们是不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.11,0:42:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}丞相所言甚是
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.61,0:42:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既如此 那就与我满饮此杯
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.02,0:42:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下官抱病 不能再饮
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.59,0:42:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请丞相见谅
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.59,0:42:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}病了 正好我这有一副
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.50,0:42:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}灵丹妙药 来人哪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.00,0:42:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.30,0:42:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}带上来
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.40,0:42:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喏
